lead_paragraph: Rowing New Zealand (RNZ) put a public dispute with one of their coaches behind them to select their largest ever Olympic squad on Friday, headlined by London 2012 champions Mahe Drysdale, Hamish Bond and Eric Murray.

headline.print_headline: Champions Headline Strong NZ Rowing Team Heading to Rio
